Periodic Table and Atomic Properties

This module provides comprehensive periodic table data and atomic properties including:
- Complete periodic table with all 118 known elements
- Atomic properties (mass, radius, electronegativity, ionization energy)
- Electron configurations and orbital filling patterns
- Isotope data and nuclear properties
- Physical and chemical properties (melting point, density, oxidation states)
- Periodic trends analysis and prediction
- Element classification (metals, nonmetals, metalloids, noble gases)
- Crystal structure and atomic packing information
- Spectroscopic data (emission lines, X-ray absorption edges)
- Historical discovery information and etymology
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors
Import "math/core/constants" as Constants
Import "data/collections/core/map" as Map

